node.text:
Drifting around on Forza Horizon 4 in a BMW 1M, with 100% exhaust sound. Hope you guys enjoy it, let me know if you want me to do more of these! I do daily Story clips w/ music, here I'll post a more unedited version!
Thanks for the support #BoostSquad ❤️
